These are Puzzles for 3x4 Level 2

.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-2-1::.
There 4 different types of food: artichoke, asparagus, blueberry, garlic
4 different pets are kept: cat, ferret, lizard, turtle
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: reggae, d&b, indie, dubstep
1. the fan of indie is on the left of the owner of the ferret##1
2. the fan of dubstep is the owner of the cat##1
3. the person eating blueberry is on the far left##1
4. the person eating artichoke is on the far right##1
5. the owner of the ferret is between the fan of indie and the person eating asparagus##2
6. the fan of d&b is the owner of the lizard##1
7. the owner of the cat is on the right of the owner of the ferret##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1     |    2    |     3     |     4      |
| Food        | blueberry | garlic  | asparagus | artichoke  |
| Pet         | turtle    | ferret  | cat       | lizard     |
| Music-Genre   | indie     | reggae | dubstep       | d&b |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-2-2::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: chess, drawing, magic-tricks, reading
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: fantasy, sports, superhero, zombie
4 different games are played: bridge, snooker, scrabble, monopoly
1. the person who's hobby is drawing is on the far left##1
2. the person playing bridge is on the right of the person who's hobby is chess##1
3. the person playing snooker is on the far left##1
4. the person playing monopoly is between the person watching zombie movies and the person who's hobby is reading##2
5. the person watching zombie movies is the person playing snooker##1
6. the person watching fantasy movies is on the left of the person playing bridge##1
7. the person watching superhero movies is the person playing scrabble##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |    2     |    3     |      4       |
| Hobby         | drawing | chess    | reading  | magic-tricks |
| Movie-Genre   | zombie  | fantasy  | sports   | superhero    |
| Game         | snooker | monopoly | bridge | scrabble      |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-2-3::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: lemonade, mirinda, sprite, tea
The people have 4 different hobbies: collecting, cooking, gardening, photography
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: baseball, soccer, sailing, handball
1. the person who's sport is soccer is between the person who's sport is handball and the person drinking mirinda##2
2. the person who's hobby is collecting is on the left of the person who's sport is baseball##1
3. the person who's hobby is cooking is on the left of the person who's hobby is photography##1
4. the person drinking sprite is on the far right##1
5. the person who's hobby is cooking is on the far left##1
6. the person who's sport is baseball is on the right of the person drinking lemonade##1
7. the person who's sport is sailing is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |      2      |     3      |     4     |
| Beverage      | mirinda | tea         | lemonade   | sprite    |
| Hobby         | cooking | photography | collecting | gardening |
| Sport   | sailing   | soccer        | handball      | baseball   |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-2-4::.
4 different games are played: backgammon, scrabble, whist, bridge
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: cricket, cycling, skateboarding, tennis
The people use 4 different means of transport: bus, car, scooter, ship
1. the person driving the scooter is on the far left##1
2. the person driving the bus is between the person driving the ship and the person playing bridge##2
3. the person playing whist is on the right of the person who's sport is cycling##1
4. the person driving the bus is on the right of the person who's sport is skateboarding##1
5. the person playing whist is on the right of the person playing backgammon##1
6. the person driving the ship is between the person who's sport is cricket and the person driving the car##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1       |    2    |     3      |   4    |
| Game   | bridge        | scrabble   | backgammon | whist |
| Sport         | skateboarding | cricket | cycling    | tennis |
| Transport     | scooter       | bus     | ship       | car    |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-2-5::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: almond-milk, fanta, lemonade, tea
The people have 4 different hobbies: gardening, puzzles, sudoku, woodworking
There are 4 different favourite colors: azure, white, aquamarine, lilac
1. the person who likes lilac is between the person drinking almond-milk and the person drinking fanta##2
2. the person who likes lilac is the person drinking tea##1
3. the person who's hobby is sudoku is on the far right##1
4. the person drinking fanta is on the left of the person drinking lemonade##1
5. the person who likes azure is on the right of the person who likes aquamarine##1
6. the person who likes aquamarine is on the right of the person who's hobby is puzzles##1
7. the person who likes lilac is between the person who likes aquamarine and the person who's hobby is gardening##2

.:: Answer ::.
|            |      1      |    2     |      3      |     4      |
| Beverage   | almond-milk | tea      | fanta       | lemonade   |
| Hobby      | gardening   | puzzles  | woodworking | sudoku     |
| Color      | white     | lilac | aquamarine        | azure |

