.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-2-11::.
There 4 different types of food: eggplant, garlic, raspberry, strawberry
There are 4 different favourite colors: mauve, purple, ebony, apricot
4 different pets are kept: dog, goat, guinea-pig, rat
1. the person eating garlic is on the right of the person eating eggplant##1
2. the owner of the guinea-pig is the person eating garlic##1
3. the owner of the dog is between the person who likes purple and the person who likes ebony##2
4. the person who likes ebony is between the owner of the dog and the person eating strawberry##2
5. the person who likes ebony is the owner of the rat##1
6. the person who likes mauve is the owner of the goat##1
7. the person who likes apricot is the owner of the dog##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1      |     2     |    3     |     4      |
| Food    | strawberry  | raspberry | eggplant | garlic     |
| Color   | mauve | ebony   | apricot  | purple    |
| Pet     | goat        | rat       | dog      | guinea-pig |

