.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-2-13::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: almond-milk, fanta, milk, water
City: hamburg, edinburgh, colone, liverpool
4 different pets are kept: ferret, hamster, pony, rabbit
1. the person drinking water is on the left of the owner of the ferret##1
2. the owner of the rabbit is between the person drinking milk and the person traveling to hamburg##2
3. the person drinking fanta is on the right of the person drinking milk##1
4. the person drinking almond-milk is the owner of the pony##1
5. the owner of the hamster is on the right of the person traveling to edinburgh##1
6. the person drinking water is the person traveling to colone##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |      1      |   2    |     3      |    4    |
| Beverage   | almond-milk | water  | milk       | fanta   |
| City      | hamburg     | colone | edinburgh | liverpool |
| Pet        | pony        | rabbit | ferret     | hamster |

