.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-2-15::.
4 different pets are kept: lizard, ferret, mouse, cat
The people have 4 different jobs:  paramedic, police-officer, project-manager, security-guard
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: biathlon, parkour, rugby, sailing
1. the owner of the mouse is the person who's sport is rugby##1
2. the person who's sport is sailing is the owner of the cat##1
3. the owner of the lizard is the security-guard##1
4. the owner of the mouse is on the far left##1
5. the person who's sport is parkour is between the paramedic and the owner of the lizard##2
6. the project-manager is on the left of the person who's sport is biathlon##1
7. the person who's sport is biathlon is between the person who's sport is sailing and the person who's sport is parkour##2

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1     |        2        |       3        |       4        |
| Pet   | mouse   | ferret           | lizard         | cat      |
| Job     | paramedic | project-manager | security-guard | police-officer |
| Sport   | rugby     | parkour         | biathlon       | sailing        |

