3. the dancer is on the far left##1
4. the person driving the subway is the librarian##1
5. the person who's birthday is in march is the person driving the subway##1
6. the person driving the taxi is between the person who's birthday is in february and the person driving the subway##2

.:: Answer ::.
|             |       1       |     2      |     3      |      4       |
| Job         | dancer        | librarian  | journalist | freelancer   |
| Birthday       | may | march | august    | february |
| Transport   | roller        | subway     | taxi       | scooter      |

